35:19.575 --> 35:21.911
<i>♪ You ain't seen nothin' yet ♪</i>

35:22.411 --> 35:25.414
<i>♪ It's gonna be a night</i>
<i>We'll never forget ♪</i>

35:25.498 --> 35:27.917
<i>♪ You ain't seen nothin' yet ♪</i>

35:28.000 --> 35:32.046
<i>♪ It's gonna be a night we'll never</i>
<i>No, never ♪</i>

35:32.130 --> 35:36.092
<i>♪ We'll never forget ♪</i>

35:36.926 --> 35:41.889
<i>♪ A night we'll never forget ♪</i>

35:48.354 --> 35:50.606
Claudius

35:59.365 --> 36:02.243
Do you know whose blood this is, Mommy?

36:03.244 --> 36:06.539
This is Jason's blood.
This is Daddy's blood.

36:07.248 --> 36:12.044
And the next blood to be spilt
will be yours.

36:12.128 --> 36:14.005
Cheryl, dear God.

36:14.797 --> 36:17.550
You've been in cahoots with Daddy's twin.

36:17.633 --> 36:20.595
You tried to kill Nana Rose,

36:20.970 --> 36:23.931
and then you shipped me off
to a ghoulish nunnery.

36:24.599 --> 36:27.018
But your depraved gambits are finished.

36:28.019 --> 36:33.900
If you so much as pluck one hair
from Nana Rose's little head...

36:35.943 --> 36:37.236
I'll end you.

36:41.657 --> 36:45.119
I burned one house down,
I'll happily burn another.

36:45.203 --> 36:47.747
Nightmare Child, what do you want from me?

36:47.997 --> 36:49.582
I wanna be emancipated.

36:50.666 --> 36:55.046
I want Thistlehouse all to myself
and my Nana.

36:57.632 --> 36:59.008
Start packing, Mommy.

37:00.927 --> 37:03.262
You and Uncle Claudius are pig-people

37:03.596 --> 37:06.724
and should live amongst the pigs.

37:16.776 --> 37:19.779
Thank you. Hello. Good to see you.

37:19.862 --> 37:22.823
Thank you. How are you?

37:28.829 --> 37:30.289
Hal. Come here.

37:34.710 --> 37:35.795
Did you bring it?

37:38.005 --> 37:38.839
Thanks.

37:49.267 --> 37:52.561
-I don't know.

37:56.857 --> 37:57.984
Fangs.

37:58.067 --> 38:01.112
I was giving Midge some last-minute notes.

38:01.195 --> 38:03.656
Hurry up. It's ten minutes to places.

38:13.374 --> 38:14.917
Hey, Ethel?

38:17.503 --> 38:19.130
I'm doing final interviews.

38:20.381 --> 38:21.215
Ethel?

38:50.244 --> 38:53.164
QED, folks, it was Ethel.

38:54.165 --> 38:55.166
What was?

38:56.042 --> 38:57.209
Uh...

38:57.293 --> 39:00.212
-Just the magazines.
-I know what you're thinking.

39:00.296 --> 39:01.130
You're wrong.

39:01.213 --> 39:04.675
-Those were for my vision board.
-It's okay. Tell me.

39:05.259 --> 39:07.511
Get out of my dressing room, Jughead.
Sounds like a guilty conscience to me.

39:12.308 --> 39:14.435
-Hey, Moose.
-Out of my way, Jug.

39:16.270 --> 39:19.732
<i>What a to-do to die today</i>
<i>at a minute or two till two</i>

39:19.815 --> 39:23.819
<i>A thing distinctly hard to say,</i>
<i>but harder still to do</i>

39:29.158 --> 39:33.454
Chuck... let me speak for the whole gang

39:33.537 --> 39:36.791
when I say that your behavior
throughout rehearsals

39:36.874 --> 39:41.003
has been nothing short of that
of a proper Victorian gentleman.

39:41.087 --> 39:41.962
Um...

39:42.922 --> 39:44.507
What does that mean?

39:45.424 --> 39:48.302
Your pariahship is officially over.

39:51.680 --> 39:52.723
Hey, Betty. Chic...

39:58.938 --> 39:59.897
you made it.

40:00.481 --> 40:04.026
-Of course. I wouldn't miss this.
Five minutes to places!

40:06.445 --> 40:11.492
You should get back to your seat, Chic.
You're not really allowed to be backstage.

40:12.618 --> 40:13.452
No problem.

40:16.831 --> 40:17.998
Break a leg, sis.

40:30.052 --> 40:34.849
♪  <i>Father Almighty</i>
<i>She's only a child ♪</i>

40:34.932 --> 40:39.437
<i>♪ But the woman is waking inside her ♪</i>

40:40.729 --> 40:45.818
<i>♪ She will be lost</i>
<i>If her passion runs wild ♪</i>

40:45.901 --> 40:49.780
<i>♪ So, I can't let her stumble and fall ♪</i>

40:51.782 --> 40:56.078
<i>♪ Maybe I do things that I can't explain ♪</i>

40:56.662 --> 41:00.749
<i>♪ But my feelings for her never change ♪</i>

41:02.001 --> 41:06.046
<i>♪ You are still my precious one ♪</i>

41:08.174 --> 41:13.637
<i>♪ Can you forgive what I've done? ♪</i>

41:16.891 --> 41:20.478
All right, Carrietta,
it's time to come out of your closet.

41:23.898 --> 41:27.568
Uh, Kevin, did you re
Why isn't she on her knees?

41:28.319 --> 41:29.695
I...

41:37.536 --> 41:40.539
-I don't think that's part of the show.
-Oh, my God.

41:40.623 --> 41:43.459
Somebody should help her.
Help her!

41:52.259 --> 41:53.260
Betty.
